hana|access-date=2019-11-19}}</ref>\n* [[Buea Seventh-day Adventist Hospital]], [[Buea]], Cameroon\n* [[Dominase Adventist Hospital]], [[Bekwai]], Ghana\n* [[Glei Adventist Eye Hospital]], [[Glei]], Togo\n* [[HART Adventist Hospital]], [[Kumasi]], Ghana<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://theheraldghana.com/seventh-day-adventist-opens-second-specialized-hospital-in-kumasi/|title=Seventh Day Adventist Opens Second Specialized Hospital In Kumasi||last=Torbizo-Kumasi|first=Samuel|date=2016-07-20|website=The Herald Ghana|access-date=2019-11-19}}</ref>\n* [[Inisa Community Medical Centre]], [[Inisa]], Nigeria\n* [[Jengre Seventh-day Adventist Hospital]], [[Jos]], Nigeria\n* [[Konkoma Seventh-day Adventist Hospital]], [[Kumasi]], Ghana\n* [[Koza Adventist Hospital]], [[Koza, Cameroon]]\n* [[Kwadaso Seventh-day Adventist Hospital]], [[Kwadaso]], Ghana\n* [[Moundou Adventist Surgical Center]], Chad\n* [[Obuasi Seventh-day Adventist Hospital]], [[Obuasi]], Ghana\n* [[Seventh-day Adventist Cooper Hospital]], [[Monrovia]], Liberia\n* [[Seventh-day Adventist Cooper Eye Center]], [[Monrovia]], Liberia\n* [[Seventh-day Adventist Hospital and Motherless Babies' Home, ABA]], [[Aba, Abia|Aba]], Nigeria\n* [[Seventh-day Adventist Hospital Ile-Ife]], [[Ife|Ile-Ife]], Nigeria\n* [[Seventh-day Adventist Hospital, Koforidua]], [[Koforidua]], Ghana\n* [[Tamale Adventist Hospital]], [[Tamale, Ghana]]\n* [[Valley View Adventist Hospital]], [[Techiman]], Ghana\n* [[Valley View University Hospital]], [[Accra]], Ghana\n* [[Waterloo Seventh-day Adventist Hospital]], [[Waterloo, Sierra Leone]]\n* [[Wiamoase Seventh-day Adventist Hospital]], [[Wiamoase]], Ghana\n\n==[[Inter-European Division of Seventh-day Adventists|Inter-European Division]]==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Hospital Name\n! Location\n! Other Name/Former Name\n! Photo\n! Ref.\n|-\n| Haus Niedersachsen Hospital \n| [[Wolfsburg]], Germany\n|\n|\n|<ref name=germany>{{Cite web|url=http://news.eud.adventist.org/en/all-news/news/go/2012-05-10/nikolassee-hospital-the-second-adventist-hospital-in-berlin-germany/|title=Nikolassee Hospital, The Second Adventist Hospital In Berlin, Germany|date=2012-05-10|website=Inter-European Division|access-date=2019-12-30}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Krankenhaus Waldfriede]] \n| [[Berlin]], Germany \n| Also called Waldfriede Hospital\n| [[File:Zehlendorf_Krankenhaus_Waldfriede.JPG|60px]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adventistreview.org/church-news/story5092-hospital-in-germany-takes-over-elderly-care-residence|title=Hospital in Germany Takes Over Elderly Care Residence|date=2017-05-15|website=Adventist Review|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adventistworld.org/adventist-center-in-its-fifth-year-helping-victims-of-female-genital-mutilation/|title= Adventist Center in Its Sixth Year Helping Victims of Female Genital Mutilation|last=Schroeder|first=Louise|date=2018-07-03|website=Adventist World|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://atoday.org/waldfriede-hospital-receives-national-german-award-supporting-victims-female-genital-mutilation/|title=German Hospital Receives National Award for Supporting Victims of Female Genital Mutilation|date=2016-05-05|website=Adventist Today|access-date=2019-01-17}}</ref>\n|-\n| La Ligniere Clinic, \n| [[Gland, Switzerland]] \n| Formerly Lake Geneva Sanitarium\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.apd.media/news/archiv/2434.html|title=Swiss Clinique La Ligniere Earns World Health Organization Designation|date=2003-06-29|website=APD|access-date=2019-05-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.eud.adventist.org/en/all-news/news/go/2017-07-01/la-ligniere-clinic-improves-its-mission/|title=La Ligni\u00e8re Clinic Improves Its Mission|date=2017-07-01|website= Inter-European Division|access-date=2019-05-16}}</ref>\n|-\n| Privalklinik Nikolassee\n| Berlin, Germany \n| Also called Nikolassee Hospital\n|\n|<ref name=germany/>\n|-\n|}\n\n==[[Trans-European Division of Seventh-day Adventists|Trans-European Divisio